bio.singa.mathematics.vectors

Interface BitVector

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Metrizable<BitVector>, MultiDimensional<BitVector>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RegularBitVector

    public interface BitVector
extends MultiDimensional<BitVector>, Metrizable<BitVector>
    A BitVector is a MultiDimensional collection of boolean values that is Metrizable with metrics for boolean-valued vectors.
